      "title": "Telecommunication services not restricted: TRCSL says",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Telecommunications Regulatory Commission of Sri Lanka (TRCSL) says it has not given directives to restrict telecommunication services in Colombo to voice calls only.",
        "In a statement, the Commission stressed that there is no truth to the statement that is currently in circulation."
      ],
